/flame off <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubrutas222.showPublicProfile?language=EN>brutas222</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/27/01 6:55:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=246.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Life after death</span><hr size=1>   Its a forum Xamael.  Are you still mad at the reverse psychology I threw at you earlier?  Again Xamael, it shouldn't matter since you are atheist.  None of this matters 'cause we will all rot.  You know I enjoy debate.  And I have NOT ONCE been afrimed by an atheist nor have a ever read a post where they agree with anyone else other than other atheists.  Don't try and feed me that bullshit about &quot;good guy bad guy&quot; shit.  I have a friend who used to be an atheist.  A hardcore atheist at that.  About your foolish claims; I have two children. Attend one of the best universities in the nation and was recognized as having an IQ level of gifted at the age of 8 years.  Sorry Xamael but your all wrong and so badly wrong that I don't feel like I've been flamed at all.  In fact I'm laughing my ass off.  I have said that I do see some good things abotu atheism.  FIND ANOTHER believer of God that would think the same.  Find some other believer in God who agrees that the man-made institution of religion has failed humankind.  Find some other believer in God who talks about the issues rather than pull some quote form the bible as proof.  Your upset Xamael.  Your not an atheist Xamael.  If you were, you wouldn't feel the need to refute my opinions.  By refuting my opinions you are suggesting that you want justice or some type of recognition.  Atheism is a rebellion against societal norms and societies recognition of acceptable behavior in the form of its greatest institution; religion.  Yep religion is a man-made institution and God is very different from religion.  You probably thought they were synonamous.  hehe, whatever Xamael.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulurikeen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lurikeen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/27/01 2:05:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=246.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Life after death</span><hr size=1> Brutas, spare us all the following sort of bull shit...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;Lurikeen, while I was reading your post I felt so sad for you. And I htink its great how you feel about life(a bit depressing though- I picture you loving people and spreading joy but stabbing yourself in the heart at the sametime)&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
