<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;We are all equal. Not because of truth but because of love. I personally believe that we are all at fault for the so-called, 'bitten apple' or 'forbidden fruit'.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
